{
  "stem": "26486.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we went-- we lived in-- in Providence, in Edgewood, Providence, And from there-- they were closing the mill on account of the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we went to New York.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Should I continue?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went to New York where Dad opened up a-- his office for making-- he was a designer in lace.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he attempted to make out lace designs, thinking that would help him during the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it didn't help him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he decided to go back, as soon as the war was finished.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He went back by himself to Calais, where he found everything demolished, all the lace mills.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My two grandfathers were owners of lace mills in Calais.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything was demolished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we stayed here in New York for a while, my mother with the four children-- Yvonne, George, Walter, May, and I-- five of us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in 19-- well, I think it was 1917 when the war finished.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think we went back about-- in '18, a little after 1918, we went back to join my dad.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there we continued to try to find work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We couldn't find work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I did like lots of teenagers, you know, a little job here, a little job there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we lived at my grandmother's house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stayed there for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my-- my dad was very lucky to get a job with the American Graves Registration in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sorry, with the-- what was the name of the organization?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The American Grave Registrations.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we all went to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to Antwerp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there we-- we had an apartment in a big hotel where they set us up, the American Grave Registration.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We stayed there for about a year.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
